{"tid":53420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺自己睇書唔係睇書而係睇字。。。","createTime":"2016-12-24T16:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T04:36:00.000Z","uid":49974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14068f562e5057c4c3453a07cf815a3db8cd60e0","tid":53420,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"一開始會好想投入個故事認真睇，但凡係一開始/中間太悶，睇睇下個腦就會停咗，完全冇吸收到書中任何嘢，只係得隻眼一路郁，好想改善下，唔知有冇人會同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa19c1ad2f9f69ab0f529b4ff52cda038d94b9b","tid":53420,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"我都有咁既問題，未搵到完美解決方法<br />\n但一邊睇一邊寫summary有幫助"},{"pid":"8b8ef826a0148978ac7920ff79e966ae27ebbe3a","tid":53420,"uid":29438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"我有時都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6712be1c72311b5992b1b48f8521bc1e1982fd","tid":53420,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n咪唔好睇住囉<br />\n對眼望住但個腦都無郁過"},{"pid":"2a0bf972eeb9a29027fd355af9b182e97a88a6f0","tid":53420,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"我察覺嗰陣會由開始發吽哣嗰到重新睇多次，然後一邊睇，一邊係個心到讀個故事出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個都係唔多上心，過幾日就忘記咗嗰故事大綱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一一次令我覺得睇書係有趣嘅係一本英文書，因為要寫book report嘅關係，所以被迫睇，但發現個故仔係非常好睇，中間睇到喊咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e23f758e2be5b87b1e6922ad42c69e94f6136b","tid":53420,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"一路睇但個腦係諗緊其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ce46f385b60821ca927f913f1e11c5bd461562","tid":53420,"uid":46565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim